{"570950":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Devilated","steam_appid":570950,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"controller_support":"full","dlc":[1789290],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unleash your Inner Evil With Style, Speed, and Savagery<\/h2><br>Meet Devilated, the bastard child of a Boomer Shooter and a Classic RPG after snorting a line of pure, uncut hyperviolence. <br><br>Shoot, ‘splode, slice, and shovel your way through a mysterious labyrinth brimming with bloodthirsty creatures. Style and savagery will be rewarded with a combo meter keeping score. Use the bodies of your foes as shields then consume them for health, slow things down with bullet time to land every shot, or equip several rocket launchers at once to show that subtlety is dead and you’re its unrepentant murderer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">*Note: <strong>This game is a slow-burner.<\/strong><\/h2> Unlock weapons, items, abilities, and get to NG+ to get powerful.<br><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/570950\/extras\/DevilatedStore_Melee.gif?t=1658137084\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:<\/strong><\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30 labyrinthian levels and 30 insane bosses.<br><\/li><li>Unlock 100+ weapons, around 70 items, and abilities like bullet time, dashing, and dual-wielding.<br><\/li><li>Huge playtime with 20 to 60 hours+ of gameplay with NG+.<br><\/li><li>Classic RPG inventory with rotatable items.<br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/570950\/extras\/DevilatedStore_Inven2.gif?t=1658137084\" \/><br><\/li><li>New game + (Slaughter rank): The enemy count is increased and keeps on increasing – face the ultimate challenge and unlock your true potential as a master of carnage.<br><\/li><li>Headbang along to our incredible Metal soundtrack.<br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/570950\/extras\/DevilatedStore_Dive.gif?t=1658137084\" \/><br><\/li><li>Equip various weapons and form you